FT  22 APR 94 / UK Company News: Benchmark recovery
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The recovery seen in the second half of the previous year at Benchmark Group
continued in the six months to December 31. Pre-tax profits for the property
investment company were Pounds 1.24m, against losses of Pounds 3.08m,
restated for FRS 3.
