<HEADLINE>
FT  22 APR 94 / Campaign Diary: Pounds 1.5m equipment haul recovered
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By KEVIN BROWN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Police in Kent have recovered stolen construction equipment worth Pounds
