Mr Davis stepped down as chairman and chief executive of Paramount last
month following the completion of the first step of the merger of Paramount
and Viacom. Paramount is now a majority-owned subsidiary of Viacom.
Mr Donald Oresman, who quit as executive vice-president, is joining Mr Davis
