to Es834bn. The bank more than doubled assets invested in unit trusts to
Es575bn. Earnings per share increased from Es47 to Es49.7.
Mr Jardim Goncalves said the first-quarter results were affected by the
setting aside of Es3bn in provisions against bad debt.
