FT  21 APR 94 / Observer: Bertie's banger
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Are the gods saying something to Bertie Aherne, Ireland's finance minister?
His IPounds 30,000 official car has just been stolen from under the nose of
his police driver. A Garda patrol car gave chase, only to be rammed - by
another stolen car.
