<HEADLINE>
FT  21 APR 94 / People: Finance moves
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Luke March, formerly deputy secretary, has been appointed group company
secretary of TSB GROUP in succession to the late Peter Rowland.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>TSB Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
